            <div type="transcript" id="J37">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Before the ice is in the pools --</l>
                    <l>Before the skaters go,</l>
                    <l>Or any cheek at nightfall</l>
                    <l>Is tarnished by the snow --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Before the fields have finished,</l>
                    <l>Before the Christmas tree,</l>
                    <l>Wonder upon wonder</l>
                    <l>Will arrive to me!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>What we touch the hems of</l>
                    <l>On a summer's day --</l>
                    <l>What is Only walking</l>
                    <l>Just a bridge away --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>That which sings so -- speaks so --</l>
                    <l>When there's no one here --</l>
                    <l>Will the frock I wept in</l>
                    <l>Answer me to wear?</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
